  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Proportion of MA-negative urine samples between the 2-week CBT text period and the 2-week control period</measure>
    <time_frame>5 weeks</time_frame>
    <description>The primary efficacy measure for this study is the difference in proportion of MA-negative urine samples between the 2-week CBT text period and the 2-week control period. Urine samples will be analyzed for MA by immunoassay with a cutoff of 1,000 ng/mL.</description>
